Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:05.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}てめぇの　あの技には
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:05.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}All I'm doing is furthering the old man's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:09.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}２つ　デッケェ弱点がある！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:09.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm not looking for any trouble. Ging-san, why do this if you don't want
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:46.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ついに　ナックルに 本気の戦いを挑んだゴン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:46.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Request x And x Wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.18,0:02:02.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴンの技に弱点があると 指摘したのだった ところで　ゴン。 ん？ あの技の名前 何て言うんだ？　こら。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.18,0:02:02.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}On August 8th at 12:00 AM, in the Hunter Association main headquarters, the voting to elect Netero's successor, Heart Is Valuable the 13th Chairman, began.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:04.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}しまった！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:04.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The rules set by Ging
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:08.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}技の名前　ちゃんと 決めてなかった気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:08.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}made all of the six hundred and sixty-one members
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:10.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジャ…　ジャンケン！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:10.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}both a candidate and voter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:18.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うわ　そのままだ。 ぐっ！ 「ジャジャン拳」か　なるほどな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:18.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}On this day, voter turnout was below the required 95%, meaning the vote had to be redone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジャンケンと必殺技を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}1) Pariston \N\N2) Cheadle \N\N3) Ickshonpe \N\N4) Botobai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:24.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジャジャンと出すみたいな 効果音とを掛けてるわけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:24.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However, the second vote Election for the 13th Chairman \N\N1) Pariston — 251 (37.9%) \N2) Cheadle — 46 \N3) Ickshonpe — 28 \N4) Botobai — 27 \N5) Mizaistom — 24
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:27.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ…　いや…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:27.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}8) Cutie, Sanbica, \NTeradein, Bushidora — 10 \N12) Loupe — 9 \N13) Linne, Biscuit — 8 \N15) Tsezguerra — 7 \N16) Knov, Kanzai — 6 \N18) Kite, Satotz — 4 \N20) Menchi, Geru, 13 others — 3 \N35) Saiyu, 11 others — 2 \N47) Gon, Hanzo, 16 others — 1 also failed to meet the requirements, Vote must be retaken because \Nrequirements were not met.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:30.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最初の「ジャ」は つっかえただけなんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:30.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Invalid — 45                    Absent — 33 \NTurnout — 88.2% and had to be redone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:34.69,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なかなか　いい名前じゃねえか！ こら！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:34.69,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Taking the results from the \Ntwo votes into consideration... First, we will have Beans-san review all ballots
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:39.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ　うん まぁ　いいや　それで。 いいのかよ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:39.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}before they are entered, to reduce \Nthe number of invalid votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:44.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴン！ てめぇの「ジャジャン拳」には ２つ　デケェ弱点がある！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:44.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Second, Hunters who violate the rules by \Nabstaining or submitting invalid votes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:47.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１つ！　溜めが長ぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:47.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}will have their licenses temporarily taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:52.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}戦闘中に 技を出すまでの数秒間ってのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:52.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Those are my two suggestions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:54.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}気が遠くなるほど長ぇぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:54.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we implement the first, \Ndo we still need the second?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:59.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そう簡単に 出せると思うなよ　こら。 分かってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:59.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Just getting rid of the invalid \Nvotes would put us over 95%.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:02.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}２つ！　危険がデケェ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:02.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I wouldn't be so sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:05.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}威力を上げようとして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:05.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Some Hunters may play hooky when they \Nlearn they can't submit invalid votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:11.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}拳にオーラを 集めりゃ集めるほど 体を守るオーラが減るだろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:11.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There are those who would trample \Non the former chairman's wishes. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:15.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もろいとこ攻撃されたら イチコロだろうが　ボケ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:15.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Drop it. You'll only waste time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}リスクは　承知の上さ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh? Did I say something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:22.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それを補うために　この１か月間 修行して来たんだ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:22.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The former chairman declared that \Na 95% turnout was required, so Hunters who submit invalid votes or \Nwon't vote are betraying his memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:27.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あらめて見ると すげぇオーラだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:27.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They just don't want to see you become chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:32.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}総量だけでいったら プロの中堅クラスと遜色ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:32.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then they should vote for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}惜しいな…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm sure there are other qualified candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:43.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}経験が足りねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:43.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is that too hard for you, with your limited \Nvocabulary and math skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}実践が少ねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I told you that you'd only waste time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:04:00.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}思いっ切りの良さは　半端ねえ 死線は　何度か乗り越えてるし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:04:00.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Before adding new rules, \NI believe we should broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:03.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}天性のもんもあるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:03.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}each candidate's message.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:06.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　ぎこちねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:06.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Besides, abstaining and submitting invalid \Nvotes are not technically violations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:10.69,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}オーラの流れが　ぎこちねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:10.69,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I fully agree with your first statement, but the second makes me \Nwonder if I heard right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:13.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おめぇが どこを守ろうとしているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:13.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I cannot believe those words came from one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:17.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これから 何をしようとしているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:17.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}of the former chairman's leading supporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:20.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}オーラの動きで 全部　分かっちまう!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:20.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The former chairman said that the difficulty of this election was D-rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:27.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ！ それを逆手にとって 少しフェイントを入れて！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:27.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Which means, for us Hunters with stars, \Nthis should be a simple task.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:33.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}打撃ポイントをずらせば…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:33.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In other words, the former chairman \Ntrusted us to handle this. Pariston, you're a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:35.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:35.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't talk! Keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:41.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ガハっ！ あうっ！ ガハっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:41.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The difficulty level is just his way of \Nexpressing his degree of trust in the Zodiacs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こうなる！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If it's F, he's challenging us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:49.69,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ…。 クソっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:49.69,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You can spin it however you want, but abstaining and submitting invalid \Nvotes don't violate any rules, scumbag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:52.69,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}完全に読まれてる オーラの流れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:52.69,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When I called them violations...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:59.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やっぱりだ　ナックルは…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:59.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was only insinuating that those \NHunters are mistaken in their manner of paying respects to the former chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:06.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さてと　そろそろ 全力で　ぶち込むぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:06.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The message is that making the election \Na success would be the right way to pay our respects to him. Then, say that during your speech!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:07.69,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何て…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:07.69,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you make it a rule, that's coercion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:13.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}死んでも恨むなよ　こら！ 何て　優しいんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:13.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is coercion such a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:14.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:14.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, I get the idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:19.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:19.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm fine with both suggestions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:27.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}言われなければ 秒殺だったかもしれない。 )
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:27.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My reasons are different than yours, but I agree that, barring \Nextraordinary circumstances, no Hunters should be abstaining \Nor submitting invalid votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:33.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして　導いてくれてる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:33.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}First things first. I hope you aren't going to say that, \Nduring that time, Hunters who
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:36.69,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうすれば　より強くなれるか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:36.69,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}have their licenses taken away \Naren't considered pro Hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:41.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}優し過ぎるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:41.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You aren't that stupid, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:49.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最初は　グ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:49.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I wouldn't think of using such underhanded \Nlogic to manipulate the vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:51.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}くっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:51.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Their licenses will be confiscated. Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}くっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:08.69,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やらせねえって 言っただろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:08.69,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Are you saying that someone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:10.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ナメんなよ　こら！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:10.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}would use the threat of a license going \Nmissing to manipulate the vote?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:14.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今のが　全力？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:14.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We can't guarantee no one will do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:19.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん？ ナメてるのは　どっちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:19.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let this be clearly recorded in the minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}真剣勝負だろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hunters who lose their licenses during the election
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:24.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}殺す気で来い　ナックル！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:24.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}will not lose their right to vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:33.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}くっ…。 最初は　グ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:33.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That way, no one can manipulate \Nthe turnout or the majority.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:43.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}行くぞ！ ジャン！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:43.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I hate to admit it, but unless we do something about \Nthe majority, not just the turnout, Pariston will keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:45.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おりゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:45.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He already seems to have secured the votes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:50.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こっちだ！ うおっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:50.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}that went to Ginta, Piyon, and Cluck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:57.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}くっ！ ハッ！ どはっ！ 最初は　グ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:57.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If our timing is wrong, there will be casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:59.69,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジャン！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:59.69,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I hate to admit it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:23.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この野郎　「ジャジャン拳」を フェイントに使いやがった 技をつぶしてやるって感じが 見え見えだったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:23.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A beast that cannot be tamed... Why did the Chairman select \Nhim as Vice Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:36.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ジャジャン拳」の弱点を 逆手にとった 敵の心理を利用した作戦だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:36.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Since I get to choose my second-in-command, choosing a yes-man wouldn't be any fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:43.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ナックルにとって ゴンの「ジャジャン拳」は　いわば 狙い球の一つ　見逃し厳禁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:43.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It should be someone I can't stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:48.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}打ち返さなければならない ど真ん中の絶好球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:48.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That is who I want at my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:56.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それが力みとなる 来たと思う瞬間 余計な力が入る 打てる　打たねば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:56.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Chairman, I still believe you made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:03.69,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それは　オーラでも 同じことが言える
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:03.69,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Young Killua has returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:07.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}術者が意図して抑えなければ オーラは　力んだ箇所へ集まり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:07.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's great...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:11.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}打とうとする瞬間 さらに大きくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:11.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When I saw his name on the list of Hunters \Nwho didn't vote, I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:15.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}術者が未熟なら　あるいは 平常心を失っていれば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:15.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:28.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:28.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's opened Testing Gates 1 through 5?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:32.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴンは　ナックルの甘さを指摘し 動揺を誘った
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:32.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Actually, his expression was what concerned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:35.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}結果　フェイントは見事　成功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:35.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He looked very distressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:37.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}恐らく　この作戦は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:37.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I couldn't bring myself to speak to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:45.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ジャジャン拳」の威力を 知っている者ほど効果がある ゴンが技を出そうとする瞬間 技の破壊力を知っている者ほど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:45.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you run into his friend there, \Ncan you relay a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:49.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「来る！」という恐怖心が 自身の平常心を削る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:49.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Ask him to help young Killua. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:52.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フェイントも より効果が高まり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:52.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}His friend is why he's upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:56.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敵が退けば　「チー」や「パー」での 追い打ちが仕掛けやすくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:56.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What? Gon-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:06.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}使いにくい技だと思っていた それが弱点だと…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:06.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Young Killua...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:32.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴンは　考えていたのか？ 弱点の克服法を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:32.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let me see Alluka. I need her power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:37.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:37.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't have time, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:41.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}思いついたんだ この戦いの中で！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:41.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll go even if you try to stop me, so come with me. It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:45.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}成長する　ものすごい速さで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:45.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No one can control Alluka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:47.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}戦いの中で！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:47.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:51.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:51.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're wrong... Brother's wrong... Alluka's a member of the family!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:58.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}早くも　「堅」を維持するのが しんどくなって来たぞ まだ２０分も 戦ってないはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:58.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She isn't a machine! As her brother, I'm asking her for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:02.69,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}動いたりしながらだから 消耗が激しいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:02.69,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}For help?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:07.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}修行での１時間が 実戦では１０分だとすると…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:07.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That child
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:11.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あと１０分足らずしか 「堅」は持たない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:11.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}is not human. You shouldn't consider
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:15.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}オーラでの攻防力が下がれば 負けは確実
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:15.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}that thing to be a member of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:18.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その前に決める
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:18.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:26.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}来いや！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:26.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That thing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:06.69,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なのに　ナックルは　まだ 余力を十分残し
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:06.69,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:18.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ジャジャン拳」は 発動準備の段階で 大量のオーラを必要とする フェイントだけでも　相当のオーラが 消費されているはず
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:18.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If someone tries to dispel the restriction \Nand covenant Gon set for himself, they'll be either repelled or killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:22.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}すでに　ゴンは 技を３回起動させている
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:22.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If Alluka hasn't changed, I'm the only one who can help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:31.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}戦ってから ２０分が経過してる もう一度　「ジャジャン拳」を 使おうとしたら あと１２分あるか　ないか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:31.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And Alluka's the only one who can save Gon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:34.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それが全力で戦える限界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:34.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Promise me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:48.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:48.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I ignore a friend I have the ability to help, \Nwouldn't I be betraying him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:53.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴン　俺に全力を出せとか ぬかしたが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:53.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:07.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}放出系の攻撃か それにしても　「グー」に比べたら 低レベル
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:07.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm sure you already know this, but no new requests have been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:11.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}根っからの強化系だな おめぇは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:11.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Who made the last wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:14.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}放出系の「パー」は 明らかにパワーダウン
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:14.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Milluki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:18.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}スピードもねえ　威力もねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:18.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He asked for the newest computer \Navailable at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:22.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この程度のレベルなら 球に仕掛けがあるはずもねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:22.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He made the wish himself in Alluka's \Npresence, so he couldn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:28.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はじき返して　しまいだ！ うりゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:28.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A computer shouldn't be that bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:33.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいこで…！ あいこ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:33.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Was it because Illumi was controlling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:40.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}球を目隠しに使い　背後へ… ヤベェ！ 「ジャジャン拳」の連続攻撃！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:40.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How could I leave my little \Nsister in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:45.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}グ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:45.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Killua, I want to go over this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:48.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うわ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:48.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When making a wish to Alluka, \Nwhat are the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:06.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}んっ　おぉ…。 ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:06.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Killua, if you can't stay calm, we're stopping now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:22.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「グー」の前に　すでに オーラを使い果たしていたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:22.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can you go over the rules for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:27.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうでなけりゃ　倒されていた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:27.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Alluka is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:36.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どこ行くんだよ　こら！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:36.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, yes... I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:38.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}帰るんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:38.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:40.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おめぇは　やんねえのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:40.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Climb the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:42.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は余裕だぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:42.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:45.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あんたはゴンが　また明日 相手になる。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:45.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Raise me up high! Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:48.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}きっと　今日みたいなわけには いかないぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:48.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There you go! Mitsuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:51.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は　シュートを倒す。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:51.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, yes? What is it, Master Alluka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:09.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ホントにやれんの？ ったりめぇだ！　こら！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:09.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes... Master Alluka's \Nface suddenly changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:11.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}明日さ…。 あ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:11.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, it's okay. I can handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:17.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あんたが勝つならいいよ 全力じゃなくても。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:17.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Alluka, lift me up high!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:21.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　もし　あんたが 力を出し切らずに負けたら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:21.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}'Kay. Up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:23.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}許さねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:23.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:28.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あんたを一生　許さねえからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:28.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}'Kay. See? She's back. Keep this a secret from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:42.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}相変わらず甘いな　お前は。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:42.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It happens after three requests are fulfilled...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:46.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敵に塩を送りまくって どうするんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:46.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yep, her eyes turn black.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:52.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}果ては　相手にまで それを非難される始末。 ＮＧＬに行く気がないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:52.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And they turn back after Alluka lifts you up high? No, then Alluka grants a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:55.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さっさと割り符を 彼らに渡したらどうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:55.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I didn't understand at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:16:01.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁ　あの２人は 受け取らないだろうがね。 てめぇ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:16:01.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So I wished for her to tell me \Nhow to turn her eyes back, and Alluka told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:08.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}テンパってねえ時は マジで偉そうだな　ったくよう。 てめぇが この１か月でやったことといや
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:08.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do you remember the exact words Alluka said?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}尾行だけだろうが　こら！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}After she grants a wish, her eyes turn white.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:16.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やるよ　明日は　俺も戦う。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:16.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And when three of her requests \Nare fulfilled, they turn black.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:32.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}安心しな　万全な体調で 明日　戦えるように
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:32.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No matter how small they are. Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:36.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}マッサージしておいたわさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:36.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Mitsuba... Carry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:38.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それより 問題は　キルアだわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:38.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't do that, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:43.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この１か月間　全く敵と 戦えなかったのは　計算外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:43.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then, Mitsuba, shake my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:47.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルア！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:47.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, um... I can't do that, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:53.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}勝負よ　私と！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:53.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then I want a piggyback ride, Mitsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:03.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうしたの!? キルア　その顔！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:03.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Come on, Master! Let's go catch some bugs. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:06.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん？　特訓だよ　ビスケとの。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:06.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then, Mitsuba, lift me up high.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:12.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}特訓？　リンチじゃなくて？ それより　お前のほうは大丈夫かよ 体調は。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:12.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't do that, either, Mast—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はぁ…　危ねえ　危ねえ。 ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Mitsuba was in the play area...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:31.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((いいこと？ 昨日のことを喋ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:31.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hasamu was in the butlers' quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:39.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}顔が　さらに その３倍になるわよさ！)) ) ありゃ　本気だった。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:39.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So two people, in different locations, were instantly crushed at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:46.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((分かったかい？ あんたの弱点))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:46.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What is happening? It's because she refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:52.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}) )
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:52.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She refused four of Alluka's requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:54.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((戦闘に関して慎重過ぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:54.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yasuha, piggyback ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:59.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あるいは　己を過小評価していると 言い換えてもいい))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:59.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:15.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((先に言っとくけど それは　あんたのせいじゃ　ない))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:15.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Master Alluka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:19.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((あんたに 戦闘を教え込んだ人物の責任))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:19.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can you make me a millionaire?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:50.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((戦闘力ってのは 環境　体調などで上下するもの))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:50.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There has been a mysterious incident \Nin which an airship transporting money
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:56.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((例えば　Ｃが絶好調なら 不調時のＤに 高確率で勝てるだろう))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:56.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}suddenly went missing, and when it \Nwas found, all the money was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:19:00.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((つまり　条件を整えれば Ａ　Ｂ　Ｃの誰もが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:19:00.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The pilot and crew members have \Nprovided baffling explanations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:03.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Ｄに勝てる潜在力を 持っているわけだわさ))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:03.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It will take a while to determine the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:06.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((それに対し　あんたの場合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:06.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:09.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敵のマックスを測ろうとする))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:09.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I couldn't help myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:13.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((そして　常に 最悪の場合を想定して戦う))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:13.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I find it hard to believe that \Nthis was just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:19.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((互角の力量を持つ敵とでも 「かなり強い」とか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:19.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When Alluka is with us... He never makes any requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:26.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「敵に　こうされたらヤバい」とか 考えちゃってる)) ((相手が少しでも格上ならば もうＮＧ))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:26.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Dad, can you let me choose the next butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:30.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((「何とか勝とう」って気持は びた一文なくなる))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:30.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So your mission is to fulfill Alluka's requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:34.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((選択は　逃げの一手 負け犬の思考))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:34.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes... I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:41.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((あんたは　これから その悪癖を押さえ込み 自分よりも強い敵に 真っ向勝負を挑む
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:41.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you clear this mission, \NI will spare you and your lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:44.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}意志の力が必要になる))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:44.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey, Kasuga...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:51.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((もしも明日 シュートを倒せなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:51.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, what is it? Give me your liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:54.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴンの元から消えなさい))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:54.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Um, that's not... You know? You won't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よし！　今度こそ　勝つぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then, Kasuga, give me your duodenum. Please wait, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:05.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フン　フン　フン！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:05.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's play a different game! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:30.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}過保護とも思えるような 戦闘育成法は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:30.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Give me your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:35.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}恐らく　キルアに対する 過剰な愛から来ている
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:35.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When three of Alluka's requests are \Nfulfilled, she'll grant one wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:46.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いびつで利己的な ゆがんだ愛 それだけに　強く　重く 非対象者に絡みつく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:46.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There probably isn't any limit \Nto the wishes she can grant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:52.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その呪縛 並大抵の努力では解けない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:52.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My guess is that she can grant any wish. Wish But the bigger the wish she grants...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:08.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私にも分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:08.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And the sacrifice isn't made by the \None whose wish was granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どう　決着がつくか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's the next person who fulfills the requests. Request 1                             Request 2
